item.title: Friday Chit Chat 2
item.description: We have another special bonus episode on Office Ladies 6.0! The Office Ladies team have a Friday chit chat to catch up on everyone’s Spring Break. Angela talks about a party she attended for Glen Powell’s new condiment line Smash Kitchen, Jenna shares about her new vacation rule of taking pictures from a digital camera, Cassi gets inspired by an impromptu Jamie Lee Curtis speech and Sam gears up to do volunteer work at Coachella...
